(3607, 'Diaphage 500mg 20 tab.', 'دايافاج 500 مجم 20 قرص', '', '4', 'Metformin hydrochloride', 'Pharopharma', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Anti-diabetic.sensitizers.biguanide', '500mg', '**Metformin immediate-release formulations**
